PrecisAppointment of JOSETTE-RENÉE LANDRY of Champlain, Ontario, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canada Foundation for Innovation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Catherine Aczel Boivie, whose term has expired.
